WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:39.672 --> 00:00:41.765
Qi Sha (Seven Killings) is the Power Star

3
00:00:41.975 --> 00:00:44.170
Po Jun (Army Breaker) is the Ruinous Star

4
00:00:44.377 --> 00:00:46.641
Tan Lang (Greedy Wolf) is the Flirting Star

5
00:00:46.846 --> 00:00:49.041
According to Chinese astrology. these three stars.

6
00:00:49.249 --> 00:00:50.876
with their changes.

7
00:00:51.084 --> 00:00:53.143
could create or destroy
that beautiful life of yours

8
00:01:42.368 --> 00:01:47.533
1994 Hong Kong

9
00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:26.531
Dad. when will you and mom

10
00:03:26.739 --> 00:03:29.003
take me to the beach?

11
00:03:29.275 --> 00:03:31.937
Hoi Yee. sweetie. in a couple of days

12
00:03:32.445 --> 00:03:33.912
Great! Mommy!

13
00:03:34.647 --> 00:03:35.511
Good girl

14
00:03:35.715 --> 00:03:36.773
After court today.

15
00:03:36.983 --> 00:03:39.144
Wong Po will spend
the rest of his life in jail

16
00:03:41.521 --> 00:03:43.512
Don't worry.
Things will be fine starting tomorrow.

17
00:04:21.394 --> 00:04:22.622
Due to insufficient evidence.

18
00:04:22.829 --> 00:04:24.524
Wong Po was acquitted

19
00:04:24.731 --> 00:04:26.961
All the charges against Wong Po

20
00:04:27.166 --> 00:04:30.761
were dropped. and he was released

21
00:04:55.728 --> 00:04:58.458
Chung...
Wah. Sum. Where's Ah Lok?

22
00:04:58.765 --> 00:04:59.163
They're all right.

23
00:04:59.365 --> 00:05:00.923
How all right? How...

24
00:05:01.134 --> 00:05:01.964
They are out of danger!

25
00:05:02.168 --> 00:05:02.964
How about the witness?

26
00:05:03.169 --> 00:05:04.431
The witness and his wife. they are dead

27
00:05:05.071 --> 00:05:07.733
That girl...

28
00:05:13.746 --> 00:05:17.307
It hurts so much...

29
00:05:31.597 --> 00:05:35.192
It hurts so much...

30
00:07:20.406 --> 00:07:21.395
Come on!

31
00:07:25.845 --> 00:07:26.675
Come on!

32
00:07:34.454 --> 00:07:36.786
Inspector Chan.
do you want to call a tow truck?

33
00:07:42.328 --> 00:07:43.727
27 calling. 27 over

34
00:07:44.530 --> 00:07:46.862
There's a car accident in Cypress Road.
Clear Water Bay.

35
00:07:47.066 --> 00:07:48.158
I'm handling it.

36
00:07:53.739 --> 00:07:55.229
The baby...

37
00:08:01.681 --> 00:08:04.582
Mrs. Wong.
this is your second miscarriage

38
00:08:05.151 --> 00:08:06.345
I'm afraid it might be habitual...

39
00:08:06.552 --> 00:08:07.883
What are you trying to say?

40
00:08:17.864 --> 00:08:19.923
I'm sorry. Inspector Chan

41
00:08:21.100 --> 00:08:23.295
I've just got your report.
Let's talk inside

42
00:08:23.503 --> 00:08:26.028
No. I'm busy.
Do you have to check my wound?

43
00:08:26.272 --> 00:08:28.365
There's no infection in the wound.
No problem there.

44
00:08:28.641 --> 00:08:29.801
Then. I won't be coming back next week

45
00:08:30.009 --> 00:08:31.203
Inspector Chan...

46
00:08:33.312 --> 00:08:35.906
I've found there's a tumor in your brain.
It's malignant

47
00:08:44.657 --> 00:08:46.818
I want to have a child with you

48
00:08:51.864 --> 00:08:52.990
We'll talk about this later

49
00:09:01.807 --> 00:09:02.705
Is it curable?

50
00:09:03.709 --> 00:09:06.405
The chance is slim.
but there's still hope

51
00:09:11.951 --> 00:09:13.077
I see

52
00:09:15.888 --> 00:09:17.185
Did you see my little girl?

53
00:09:24.263 --> 00:09:26.731
What are you doing. sir?

54
00:09:30.036 --> 00:09:31.765
I'll treat you to a candy

55
00:09:33.239 --> 00:09:35.400
You'll have the orange one.
and I'll have the green one

56
00:09:40.646 --> 00:09:41.874
What's your name?

57
00:09:42.848 --> 00:09:44.179
Hoi Yee

58
00:09:50.056 --> 00:09:53.822
You listen. as long as I'm alive.
I'm gonna nail you

59
00:10:37.269 --> 00:10:38.293
Wah

60
00:10:39.905 --> 00:10:41.065
I've got a tumor

61
00:10:44.777 --> 00:10:45.937
Where?

62
00:10:48.180 --> 00:10:49.477
In my brain

63
00:10:52.284 --> 00:10:53.478
Can it be cured?

64
00:10:54.086 --> 00:10:55.348
No idea

65
00:10:56.622 --> 00:10:57.884
That means you're gonna be fine

66
00:11:07.233 --> 00:11:08.564
Back to work when you finish

67
00:11:39.665 --> 00:11:41.633
One after another. hands on the stairs!

68
00:11:44.737 --> 00:11:46.364
Don't run! Stop...

69
00:11:46.872 --> 00:11:47.930
Stand still!

70
00:11:52.144 --> 00:11:53.042
Bastards!

71
00:11:55.448 --> 00:11:56.506
Tell me!

72
00:11:57.883 --> 00:11:58.907
Get down. over there!

73
00:11:59.418 --> 00:12:00.248
Get down!

74
00:12:02.254 --> 00:12:03.653
Chung has seen a doctor

75
00:12:05.224 --> 00:12:07.886
The doctor says he has cancer

76
00:12:09.395 --> 00:12:10.692
In the brain

77
00:12:18.104 --> 00:12:19.162
Incurable

78
00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:23.164
Tell him not to worry

79
00:12:24.276 --> 00:12:26.107
We'll fix things for him

80
00:12:31.183 --> 00:12:33.845
You go undercover.
After that. you'd get promoted fast

81
00:12:35.321 --> 00:12:37.016
I'm not afraid of going undercover

82
00:12:39.358 --> 00:12:40.882
You want me to hang out with Wong Po.

83
00:12:41.660 --> 00:12:43.252
but it's no good messing with him

84
00:12:43.696 --> 00:12:46.028
Once I get near him.
there's no turning back

85
00:12:47.166 --> 00:12:48.724
Wong Po is a nut case

86
00:12:50.903 --> 00:12:52.666
All of you have had a taste of him.

87
00:12:53.405 --> 00:12:54.269
We're not afraid.

88
00:12:54.473 --> 00:12:55.872
If we could.
we'll be glad to do it ourselves

89
00:12:56.075 --> 00:12:58.407
Why bother to be a cop if
you're so afraid. Be a baker

90
00:12:58.611 --> 00:13:00.010
I'm sure I can find someone
who is willing to do this

91
00:13:00.312 --> 00:13:01.370
I'm sure you can't

92
00:13:02.515 --> 00:13:03.675
Kid. don't be so cocky!

93
00:13:04.483 --> 00:13:06.781
For a cop. death is not the worst thing

94
00:13:07.953 --> 00:13:09.511
The worst thing is
to be bullied by the bad guys

95
00:13:09.755 --> 00:13:12.622
Trust me.
I won't let anything happen to my men

96
00:13:28.808 --> 00:13:33.802
THREE YEARS LATER

97
00:13:39.351 --> 00:13:40.079
What now?

98
00:13:40.286 --> 00:13:41.617
You're retiring in two days.

99
00:13:41.821 --> 00:13:43.220
Why do you have to give me a hard time?

100
00:13:43.823 --> 00:13:44.812
Let's not talk about that

101
00:13:46.892 --> 00:13:47.950
Inspector Ma is coming.

102
00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:50.025
Talk to him about
the hand-over of your team

103
00:13:50.596 --> 00:13:51.426
I have to go. I've got work to do

104
00:13:51.630 --> 00:13:53.495
You don't talk to me
about your work anymore

105
00:13:54.066 --> 00:13:55.328
You'll know when it is done

106
00:13:56.769 --> 00:13:58.031
I know without your telling me

107
00:13:58.604 --> 00:13:59.696
You've been at war
with Wong Po for years.

108
00:13:59.905 --> 00:14:01.031
Can you manage to get him?

109
00:14:01.240 --> 00:14:03.367
He is getting bigger.
while you get more screwed-up than ever

110
00:14:03.576 --> 00:14:06.477
Please. don't make any trouble
before you retire

111
00:14:07.580 --> 00:14:08.911
Should I stop working before I retire?

112
00:14:09.481 --> 00:14:10.448
Are you not waiting
for your retirement as well?

113
00:14:11.584 --> 00:14:14.075
Show me some respect.
I'm your boss after all!

114
00:14:14.553 --> 00:14:15.884
Since I respect my job.

115
00:14:16.255 --> 00:14:17.654
I can't spare any respect for you

116
00:14:47.152 --> 00:14:48.710
Did you see our new boss?

117
00:14:49.321 --> 00:14:50.345
He used to be real cool.

118
00:14:50.556 --> 00:14:52.421
He bashed a suspect into a halfwit
with one single punch

119
00:14:53.726 --> 00:14:54.988
Bullshit! Bluffing!

120
00:14:55.794 --> 00:14:56.692
It's true

121
00:15:22.721 --> 00:15:24.655
Put on a good show.
to celebrate my retirement

122
00:15:32.598 --> 00:15:33.360
Police! Freeze!

123
00:15:33.565 --> 00:15:34.930
Police! Stand still!

124
00:16:57.883 --> 00:16:58.679
Lok

125
00:17:00.486 --> 00:17:01.418
Is everything all right?

126
00:17:01.653 --> 00:17:02.585
Everything's fine

127
00:17:04.957 --> 00:17:06.117
Come over to help me

128
00:17:17.936 --> 00:17:19.870
Ourjoint was wiped out by the cops

129
00:17:20.839 --> 00:17:22.170
We've lost both the stuff and the money

130
00:17:27.513 --> 00:17:28.070
The same cops again?

131
00:17:28.280 --> 00:17:29.338
Yes

132
00:18:10.289 --> 00:18:12.257
Well. what are you up to?

133
00:18:12.458 --> 00:18:13.220
Something happened?

134
00:18:13.425 --> 00:18:16.588
It's a sunny day. Let's get a tan

135
00:18:18.363 --> 00:18:19.762
I didn't bring my swimming trunks

136
00:18:20.365 --> 00:18:23.232
None of us did. Welcome to our team.

137
00:18:26.839 --> 00:18:28.067
My men are not bad

138
00:18:30.008 --> 00:18:31.100
Who is the most able?

139
00:18:31.710 --> 00:18:32.768
Everyone of them is able

140
00:18:33.345 --> 00:18:35.176
Words are empty.
You'll get to know them

141
00:18:41.653 --> 00:18:45.180
Dad. he threw the ball into the sea!

142
00:18:45.657 --> 00:18:46.681
My goddaughter

143
00:18:47.860 --> 00:18:50.192
Her parents were killed by Wong Po

144
00:18:50.762 --> 00:18:52.389
You know about that case three years ago

145
00:18:53.966 --> 00:18:55.593
She was so scared
that she couldn't remember a thing

146
00:18:57.102 --> 00:18:59.935
I want to take care of her.
but time is running out

147
00:19:02.941 --> 00:19:04.431
Nothing is for certain

148
00:19:06.612 --> 00:19:09.046
You won't understand until the last day

149
00:19:13.152 --> 00:19:15.814
Look at him. He seems conceited

150
00:19:17.623 --> 00:19:20.888
Don't say that. he's going to be our boss

151
00:19:21.426 --> 00:19:23.621
Boss? Boss my foot?

152
00:19:24.496 --> 00:19:25.656
You're gonna work under him?

153
00:19:28.400 --> 00:19:29.890
Don't tell Chung.

154
00:19:30.836 --> 00:19:32.201
we're going to
take care of his little girl

155
00:19:36.975 --> 00:19:38.943
Wah. the day after tomorrow
will be Father's Day

156
00:19:39.144 --> 00:19:40.873
What kind of present. do you think.
my daughter will give me?

157
00:19:41.947 --> 00:19:44.074
Your wife and daughter
left more than 10 years ago

158
00:19:44.316 --> 00:19:46.181
My daughter is back

159
00:19:46.552 --> 00:19:48.918
She called me this morning.
asking to see the night after tomorrow

160
00:20:04.036 --> 00:20:05.435
In two days. this will be your turf

161
00:20:06.238 --> 00:20:09.503
There're so many blocks in this division.
I can't manage them all

162
00:20:10.542 --> 00:20:12.305
The important thing is
to know who is the toughest

163
00:20:12.778 --> 00:20:14.336
Then. you go after him

164
00:20:15.981 --> 00:20:17.380
Everybody knows you can fight

165
00:20:19.017 --> 00:20:20.279
It's only hearsay

166
00:20:26.658 --> 00:20:27.886
Wong Po says...

167
00:20:29.027 --> 00:20:31.018
he's the boss here after midnight

168
00:20:33.999 --> 00:20:35.227
I've heard about it

169
00:20:44.576 --> 00:20:45.873
Hey! What're you doing?

170
00:20:46.278 --> 00:20:48.542
What's going on? Stop!

171
00:21:11.803 --> 00:21:13.532
What's up?

172
00:21:20.412 --> 00:21:23.074
It was you who threw the bottle. Right?

173
00:21:25.284 --> 00:21:26.046
Back off! Back off!

174
00:21:26.251 --> 00:21:27.047
Police!

175
00:21:27.252 --> 00:21:28.981
Officer. is throwing bottles a crime?
Stand still!

176
00:21:29.187 --> 00:21:30.449
Frisking me? Stop that!

177
00:21:33.759 --> 00:21:34.851
What's this?

178
00:21:35.927 --> 00:21:36.791
Get up!

179
00:21:43.268 --> 00:21:44.326
Take off your shoes

180
00:21:45.237 --> 00:21:46.261
Take them off

181
00:21:53.045 --> 00:21:54.171
Your socks too

182
00:21:58.984 --> 00:21:59.882
Get up

183
00:22:01.119 --> 00:22:02.711
Get up

184
00:22:06.458 --> 00:22:07.618
Take one step backwards

185
00:22:10.128 --> 00:22:11.425
Take one step backwards

186
00:22:17.169 --> 00:22:18.158
One more step

187
00:22:27.245 --> 00:22:28.405
Start skipping

188
00:22:28.780 --> 00:22:29.337
I say skip!

189
00:22:29.548 --> 00:22:30.845
Skip my ass!

190
00:22:40.492 --> 00:22:41.652
Stand still!

191
00:23:17.562 --> 00:23:18.927
Want to pull an impressive act?

192
00:23:20.198 --> 00:23:23.326
Fatso. you'll be dealing with me.
starting tomorrow

193
00:23:24.302 --> 00:23:27.237
Fine. I'm looking forward to that

194
00:24:40.879 --> 00:24:43.939
Trust me.
I won't let anything happen to my men

195
00:25:58.023 --> 00:25:58.717
What do you want?

196
00:25:58.924 --> 00:25:59.856
To report a crime

197
00:26:00.058 --> 00:26:01.457
Go downstairs!

198
00:26:02.060 --> 00:26:03.425
A murder case

199
00:26:04.329 --> 00:26:04.954
What?

200
00:26:05.163 --> 00:26:07.393
I was shooting the lagoon monster...
and had accidentally taped a murder

201
00:26:08.333 --> 00:26:09.322
Give me that!

202
00:26:22.280 --> 00:26:23.542
Hold on! Don't move!

203
00:26:56.114 --> 00:26:59.015
A kid brought in this tape.
There are some very clear shots

204
00:27:26.945 --> 00:27:27.969
Shit!

205
00:27:29.114 --> 00:27:31.207
Bring that bastard Wong Po in

206
00:27:32.283 --> 00:27:35.013
What for? He didn't kill the man

207
00:27:38.857 --> 00:27:41.758
Erase the part of the gunshot.
People can't tell from the rest

208
00:27:47.632 --> 00:27:49.998
Lok. go get that prick

209
00:27:53.972 --> 00:27:58.272
You take care of the boy
who brought in the tape

210
00:27:58.476 --> 00:27:59.408
No problem

211
00:28:01.946 --> 00:28:03.470
Call the uniformed for support
and arrest Wong Po

212
00:28:04.182 --> 00:28:05.649
How about Inspector Ma?
Should we inform him?

213
00:28:11.823 --> 00:28:13.256
Hiding something from me?

214
00:28:14.092 --> 00:28:15.059
Take a look at this yourself

215
00:28:28.039 --> 00:28:29.506
Officially. you won't be
not on duty till tomorrow.

216
00:28:29.908 --> 00:28:30.932
You don't have to go

217
00:28:31.509 --> 00:28:32.339
Let's go

218
00:28:33.712 --> 00:28:36.010
Give me a chance to pick up more.
I'm coming with you

219
00:28:44.689 --> 00:28:45.621
Is there another copy of the tape?

220
00:28:45.824 --> 00:28:47.052
No. no...

221
00:28:47.258 --> 00:28:47.690
No?

222
00:28:47.892 --> 00:28:49.450
No. So many tapes here. No?

223
00:28:50.161 --> 00:28:52.493
Don't take my tapes. They are mine.

224
00:28:54.132 --> 00:28:56.999
I saw that man killing the guy.
I could be a witness if you want

225
00:28:57.202 --> 00:28:59.796
It wasn't that man who did it.
It was the fat guy!

226
00:29:00.004 --> 00:29:01.403
Really? It was the fat guy!

227
00:29:01.606 --> 00:29:02.095
Fat guy?

228
00:29:02.307 --> 00:29:04.400
Are you clear? The fat guy!

229
00:29:16.087 --> 00:29:16.985
Wong Po!

230
00:29:21.159 --> 00:29:22.888
You are suspected to
be involved in a murder case.

231
00:29:23.161 --> 00:29:24.025
You are now under arrest

232
00:29:24.229 --> 00:29:25.423
You again?

233
00:29:25.764 --> 00:29:27.288
Today is my son's one month's birthday.
Don't make any trouble.

234
00:29:28.733 --> 00:29:29.961
Today is the memorial day
of one of my men

235
00:29:30.335 --> 00:29:30.960
Follow me down to the station

236
00:30:24.155 --> 00:30:25.179
The fat guy shot the man!

237
00:30:25.390 --> 00:30:28.257
The fat guy shot the man...
The fat guy...

238
00:30:28.526 --> 00:30:29.185
You are nuts!

239
00:30:29.394 --> 00:30:32.090
The fat guy shot the man...

240
00:30:35.400 --> 00:30:38.062
Is this a studio?
You think you are an artist?

241
00:31:06.564 --> 00:31:08.691
They have the right
to detain you for 48 hours

242
00:31:09.500 --> 00:31:10.592
Give me the phone

243
00:31:14.772 --> 00:31:18.538
You can't make any phone call.
Ask your lawyer to do that for you

244
00:31:18.776 --> 00:31:20.004
Take it. if you dare!

245
00:31:29.387 --> 00:31:31.355
Hi. honey! Hello?

246
00:31:31.689 --> 00:31:32.781
You can't pick me up?

247
00:31:33.224 --> 00:31:34.623
Are you all right?

248
00:31:37.328 --> 00:31:40.388
Baby is one month old today.
and it's your first father's day

249
00:31:41.766 --> 00:31:42.926
You cannot come?

250
00:31:43.134 --> 00:31:44.533
Let me talk to the baby

251
00:31:45.937 --> 00:31:47.427
Dad wants to talk to you

252
00:31:49.707 --> 00:31:53.643
Precious. daddy misses you

253
00:31:59.017 --> 00:32:01.247
Honey. you're all right. aren't you?

254
00:32:02.954 --> 00:32:04.319
Take the baby home and wait for me there

255
00:32:09.794 --> 00:32:10.920
I want to get out today

256
00:32:11.462 --> 00:32:12.394
I'll think of something

257
00:32:25.476 --> 00:32:28.377
Lok. let us handle that

258
00:32:30.081 --> 00:32:31.378
Tell Wah that we've got that guy

259
00:32:32.283 --> 00:32:34.251
Now that we have taken Wong Po in.
there will be chaos

260
00:32:35.253 --> 00:32:37.380
Officially. you'd be on duty tomorrow.
Don't bother with this now

261
00:32:37.789 --> 00:32:39.689
Starting tomorrow.
I'll work with you on this case

262
00:32:41.492 --> 00:32:43.460
Did he tell you what he was going to do?

263
00:32:44.696 --> 00:32:45.685
No

264
00:32:46.965 --> 00:32:49.160
He won't even tell me;
can't expect him to tell you

265
00:32:49.434 --> 00:32:51.459
These guys are too impetuous.
It's not good.

266
00:32:51.936 --> 00:32:52.994
You should try restraining them a bit

267
00:32:54.205 --> 00:32:57.140
Remember! Charge him if you've
got evidence. If not. let him go.

268
00:34:25.263 --> 00:34:26.230
Trying to run away

269
00:34:32.270 --> 00:34:33.066
Go to hell!

270
00:34:58.930 --> 00:34:59.760
Run!

271
00:35:09.540 --> 00:35:12.407
Don't hit me

272
00:35:22.320 --> 00:35:23.480
Jump

273
00:35:24.188 --> 00:35:25.212
Jump

274
00:35:28.526 --> 00:35:29.686
Bastard!

275
00:36:57.682 --> 00:36:59.411
Keep fighting!

276
00:37:08.726 --> 00:37:10.318
I'll shoot you!

277
00:37:12.029 --> 00:37:13.189
Wah

278
00:37:19.670 --> 00:37:20.659
Are you out of your mind?

279
00:37:22.673 --> 00:37:24.106
That guy got my man killed

280
00:37:24.308 --> 00:37:25.502
And you killed him for that.

281
00:37:25.710 --> 00:37:27.007
Can a cop do whatever he pleases?

282
00:37:27.311 --> 00:37:28.209
We didn't see anything

283
00:37:28.579 --> 00:37:30.046
We only saw how you let
the suspect fall to his death

284
00:37:30.948 --> 00:37:32.575
You want to frame me? Right?

285
00:37:32.917 --> 00:37:34.043
He's one of us!

286
00:37:36.487 --> 00:37:37.784
You ever treated me as one of you?

287
00:37:40.157 --> 00:37:42.125
So what? We're not buddies

288
00:37:42.326 --> 00:37:43.793
Do we have to tell you everything?

289
00:37:45.463 --> 00:37:46.589
What do you want?

290
00:37:47.932 --> 00:37:49.763
This is none of your business.
Why did you come?

291
00:37:50.401 --> 00:37:51.629
You don't even trust your own men

292
00:37:54.071 --> 00:37:54.901
You want to frame Wong Po

293
00:37:55.106 --> 00:37:56.164
Yes!

294
00:37:57.475 --> 00:38:00.672
If that man didn't die.
Wong Po would go scot-free

295
00:38:01.212 --> 00:38:02.406
I'd like to get Wong Po too.

296
00:38:02.613 --> 00:38:04.410
but not the way you do it

297
00:38:05.082 --> 00:38:06.913
I. myself. am responsible for this

298
00:38:08.753 --> 00:38:11.779
I only have one wish. that is.
to put Wong Po behind bars

299
00:38:11.989 --> 00:38:13.388
You want to take it all on yourself?

300
00:38:14.292 --> 00:38:16.192
Do you want to put all of us in jail

301
00:38:16.427 --> 00:38:18.190
And let that bastard go scot-free?

302
00:38:18.529 --> 00:38:19.928
Do you know what is right
and what is wrong?

303
00:38:20.131 --> 00:38:21.029
You are definitely in the wrong!

304
00:38:21.232 --> 00:38:23.257
Why did you smash the suspect so hard
that he turned into a half-wit?

305
00:38:23.467 --> 00:38:26.027
Because you knew he had ruined many
people's lives; and it served him right!

306
00:38:27.071 --> 00:38:28.504
That time.
the whole police force was behind you

307
00:38:29.974 --> 00:38:33.466
You tell me.
What is right and what is wrong?

308
00:38:45.156 --> 00:38:46.316
There's no turning back now

309
00:38:47.992 --> 00:38:50.483
Turn a blind eye to this.
I won't give you any trouble

310
00:39:32.470 --> 00:39:34.768
Strike! Strike... Punch him!

311
00:39:35.172 --> 00:39:40.405
Duck! Duck...

312
00:39:40.611 --> 00:39:41.771
Cover yourself!

313
00:39:42.646 --> 00:39:45.410
Kick! Kick... and cover yourself!

314
00:39:45.683 --> 00:39:47.947
Strike! Strike!

315
00:39:48.152 --> 00:39:49.312
Kick!

316
00:40:09.073 --> 00:40:10.506
You know how many men can a gun kill?

317
00:40:10.708 --> 00:40:11.675
Eat shit!

318
00:40:16.480 --> 00:40:18.072
Strike! Strike...

319
00:40:18.282 --> 00:40:20.477
Don't strike! Kick! Kick...

320
00:40:20.684 --> 00:40:22.914
Kick him! Kick!

321
00:40:27.391 --> 00:40:28.358
I've won!

322
00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:30.492
And you suck big time!

323
00:40:30.694 --> 00:40:31.422
One more game

324
00:40:31.629 --> 00:40:32.857
Come on. one more game...

325
00:40:38.869 --> 00:40:40.029
You're a loser

326
00:40:40.237 --> 00:40:42.205
You say you're gonna beat me every week

327
00:40:42.406 --> 00:40:44.806
You say you'd try harder
and play a better game every week

328
00:40:45.142 --> 00:40:47.303
But you lose every time you come back

329
00:40:48.145 --> 00:40:49.635
A born loser

330
00:40:50.314 --> 00:40:51.906
I'm not as gifted as you

331
00:40:52.349 --> 00:40:55.375
You have to duck when people punch you

332
00:40:55.820 --> 00:40:56.912
Every week...

333
00:40:57.121 --> 00:40:58.611
Don't spend it all at once

334
00:40:59.590 --> 00:41:01.854
You say you'd try harder every week

335
00:41:02.092 --> 00:41:04.026
But you lose every week

336
00:41:04.995 --> 00:41:05.962
See you next week

337
00:41:08.666 --> 00:41:10.657
Try harder next week

338
00:41:17.141 --> 00:41:18.199
I killed that man.
and I've come to turn myself in.

339
00:41:18.409 --> 00:41:19.307
Arrest me. jerk!

340
00:41:19.510 --> 00:41:20.602
Shut your trap!

341
00:41:20.911 --> 00:41:22.503
I did it. Take me in

342
00:41:22.713 --> 00:41:24.305
Arrest me! Why don't you arrest me?

343
00:41:24.515 --> 00:41:27.382
All you cops listen.
I am responsible for the case

344
00:41:44.702 --> 00:41:45.930
What did you do?

345
00:41:46.370 --> 00:41:47.268
Shut up!

346
00:41:53.010 --> 00:41:54.034
File all their reports!

347
00:42:18.636 --> 00:42:19.534
Speak

348
00:42:19.737 --> 00:42:20.999
Who told you you could use the phone?

349
00:42:21.405 --> 00:42:22.429
Give me the phone!

350
00:42:25.476 --> 00:42:26.636
Give it to me!

351
00:42:33.684 --> 00:42:35.584
Let go! Let go!

352
00:42:37.054 --> 00:42:38.043
Get the keys!

353
00:42:49.300 --> 00:42:50.733
After tonight. you are done for

354
00:42:52.202 --> 00:42:54.193
You assholes won't get out
of this station alive

355
00:43:16.927 --> 00:43:18.758
We don't have enough evidence
to charge Wong Po

356
00:43:24.802 --> 00:43:25.962
Go get some evidence to nail him

357
00:43:27.004 --> 00:43:28.494
We haven't recovered the gun
that killed Ah Wai

358
00:43:29.139 --> 00:43:32.131
Get me a Chinese Tokarev pistol.
Fire a shot and take the bullet case

359
00:43:32.443 --> 00:43:33.933
Replace it with the one
in the property room

360
00:43:34.712 --> 00:43:35.679
I'll do it

361
00:43:47.524 --> 00:43:48.718
This is Ah Lok

362
00:43:49.960 --> 00:43:51.222
You've got guns?

363
00:43:52.029 --> 00:43:54.862
Chinese Tok. How long does it take?

364
00:43:57.134 --> 00:43:58.431
Waiting for his reply

365
00:44:06.543 --> 00:44:07.305
Hello?

366
00:44:07.511 --> 00:44:09.706
Dad. happy Father's Day

367
00:44:12.783 --> 00:44:13.841
Thank you

368
00:44:15.252 --> 00:44:16.685
I can't come so soon

369
00:44:17.321 --> 00:44:18.618
OK. I'll be there

370
00:44:19.923 --> 00:44:21.322
You'll wait for me. no matter what

371
00:44:22.393 --> 00:44:25.055
All right. I'll call you again. sweetie

372
00:44:25.496 --> 00:44:26.656
Fine. goodbye

373
00:44:28.499 --> 00:44:29.625
I'm sorry

374
00:44:36.740 --> 00:44:37.604
Hello?

375
00:44:37.975 --> 00:44:39.670
Godfather. you've finished work?

376
00:44:40.878 --> 00:44:42.209
Godfather is still working

377
00:44:42.513 --> 00:44:44.674
Why don't you take
a day off on Father's Day?

378
00:44:45.916 --> 00:44:48.146
I can't. I simply can't.

379
00:44:54.892 --> 00:44:56.154
Where's your old man?

380
00:44:58.262 --> 00:44:59.092
Dead

381
00:45:04.101 --> 00:45:05.500
I consider mine dead as well

382
00:45:09.273 --> 00:45:10.035
Wait for me

383
00:45:10.240 --> 00:45:11.969
Don't be late then

384
00:45:12.176 --> 00:45:12.938
Bye

385
00:45:26.857 --> 00:45:27.789
Hello?

386
00:45:30.160 --> 00:45:31.218
Fine

387
00:45:32.629 --> 00:45:33.891
They have a gun. I'll go get it

388
00:45:34.431 --> 00:45:35.261
I'll come with you

389
00:45:38.502 --> 00:45:39.560
Happy Father's Day

390
00:45:51.248 --> 00:45:53.739
Master Po. we've got the kid
who reported the case

391
00:45:54.118 --> 00:45:55.244
He's got a copy of the videotape

392
00:45:55.886 --> 00:45:56.682
Jack. are you there yet?

393
00:45:56.887 --> 00:45:57.876
Yes

394
00:46:08.232 --> 00:46:11.599
My family is in Brazil.
I haven't seen them for a long time

395
00:46:12.903 --> 00:46:13.870
How long have you been in the force?

396
00:46:15.038 --> 00:46:16.062
Seven years

397
00:46:18.142 --> 00:46:20.667
Inspector Ma. have you ever
thought of leaving the force?

398
00:46:20.878 --> 00:46:21.708
No

399
00:46:22.479 --> 00:46:25.312
From the first day I became a cop.
I've never thought of quitting

400
00:46:42.699 --> 00:46:43.996
My daughter is leaving tomorrow

401
00:46:45.502 --> 00:46:46.969
She wants to see me and
it doesn't happen everyday

402
00:46:48.672 --> 00:46:50.037
If I don't see her today...

403
00:46:50.908 --> 00:46:52.136
I'm afraid I won't have
the chance again in my life

404
00:46:53.811 --> 00:46:55.938
It's all about fate.
No exception for father and daughter

405
00:46:56.647 --> 00:46:57.136
Even if you have the chance.
you can't fight your fate.

406
00:46:57.347 --> 00:46:58.644
One can't really complain

407
00:47:01.018 --> 00:47:02.042
Wah

408
00:47:03.821 --> 00:47:05.618
Do you think it'll be
all right to go out now?

409
00:47:08.792 --> 00:47:10.282
If they draw their swords.
you draw your gun

410
00:47:10.928 --> 00:47:13.260
If they draw their guns.
together we have two guns

411
00:47:14.998 --> 00:47:16.397
If you really want to go.
I'll go with you

412
00:48:12.456 --> 00:48:14.583
7.000 is not enough.
We want 70.000

413
00:48:15.425 --> 00:48:16.619
You want to play with me?

414
00:48:16.994 --> 00:48:17.961
Do you want the gun or not?

415
00:48:24.501 --> 00:48:26.025
They're the only ones who've got a gun

416
00:48:26.670 --> 00:48:28.399
And they are also the only ones
not connected with Wong Po

417
00:48:32.209 --> 00:48:33.335
I'll go get the money

418
00:48:49.493 --> 00:48:50.824
Give this to your big boss

419
00:48:52.229 --> 00:48:53.389
Ask him. if you have any question

420
00:48:59.269 --> 00:49:02.534
"Chung. Wai is coming with me
to Statue Square to see my daughter"

421
00:49:02.873 --> 00:49:04.033
"I'll be right back"

422
00:49:43.647 --> 00:49:44.705
Say hello to Daddy

423
00:49:47.451 --> 00:49:49.783
I'm still working. I'll be back soon

424
00:50:08.872 --> 00:50:10.100
Chan Kwok Chung!

425
00:50:58.655 --> 00:51:00.282
Can't find him. Sir

426
00:51:00.490 --> 00:51:01.388
Keep on searching

427
00:51:02.426 --> 00:51:04.189
Uncle Ba. have you seen Chan Kwok Chung?

428
00:51:04.494 --> 00:51:05.961
I haven't seen him. Sir

429
00:52:42.392 --> 00:52:43.859
Police! Stop!

430
00:52:47.797 --> 00:52:49.128
I told you to stop!

431
00:56:13.503 --> 00:56:14.231
Hello?

432
00:56:14.437 --> 00:56:15.904
Ah Lok got whacked

433
00:56:26.449 --> 00:56:29.247
They blew my cover.
and I can't get out of the station now

434
00:56:30.086 --> 00:56:31.883
Wah and Sum are in Statue Square

435
00:56:32.422 --> 00:56:33.753
Go now to help them out

436
00:56:38.361 --> 00:56:40.158
Let's do a personality quiz?

437
00:56:41.831 --> 00:56:44.061
If you have only one more day to live

438
00:56:44.434 --> 00:56:45.765
what would you do?

439
00:56:47.837 --> 00:56:49.896
I want to spend it with you
and your mom very much

440
00:56:51.307 --> 00:56:53.832
If you plan to spend it
with someone you love.

441
00:56:54.077 --> 00:56:55.738
you are a sentimental person

442
00:57:03.386 --> 00:57:04.080
If you...

443
00:57:04.287 --> 00:57:05.982
I really want to spend it with you

444
00:57:06.389 --> 00:57:07.913
Let me finish first

445
00:57:08.124 --> 00:57:10.490
If you want to try your luck
by staking everything.

446
00:57:10.860 --> 00:57:12.953
you are a person who doesn't keep
his place and goes beyond his bounds

447
00:57:13.630 --> 00:57:17.464
If you decide to spend the time as usual.
without telling anyone.

448
00:57:17.734 --> 00:57:19.565
you have a very strong personality

449
00:57:20.036 --> 00:57:22.004
They don't have your answer here

450
00:57:23.573 --> 00:57:24.631
Joey

451
00:57:25.975 --> 00:57:27.101
Are you still mad with me?

452
00:57:28.311 --> 00:57:30.506
Mad? I don't think about it now

453
00:57:30.814 --> 00:57:34.807
And you should stop thinking too much.
It won't help

454
00:57:35.018 --> 00:57:36.610
Just be happy and smile

455
00:57:53.169 --> 00:57:56.798
Brother Chung. I don't know
if you are doing the right thing

456
00:57:57.040 --> 00:57:57.938
But I trust you

457
00:58:04.280 --> 00:58:05.304
Thanks

458
00:58:21.264 --> 00:58:22.162
Hello?

459
00:58:22.599 --> 00:58:24.829
Mom. this is Wah

460
00:58:25.902 --> 00:58:27.062
What is it?

461
00:58:30.139 --> 00:58:31.197
Nothing

462
00:58:32.509 --> 00:58:35.205
How is he? Still in the hospital?

463
00:58:36.279 --> 00:58:37.576
Is he still alive?

464
00:58:38.147 --> 00:58:40.638
You always want him to die

465
00:58:41.084 --> 00:58:43.177
He passed away last month

466
00:58:44.854 --> 00:58:47.084
It doesn't matter
who's right or who's wrong...

467
00:58:47.657 --> 00:58:50.125
You don't have anyone
to fight with anymore

468
00:58:50.760 --> 00:58:53.354
If you want to pay
your last respects. go ahead

469
00:58:54.397 --> 00:58:56.661
Nothing else? That's it

470
00:59:11.648 --> 00:59:12.842
Here's a gift for you

471
00:59:14.517 --> 00:59:15.415
What is it?

472
00:59:15.952 --> 00:59:18.546
You always want me to tell you.
Take a guess

473
00:59:21.324 --> 00:59:23.417
Try to think what I would
give you for Father's Day

474
00:59:24.827 --> 00:59:26.294
Bye See you

475
01:00:38.601 --> 01:00:39.590
Wah

476
01:00:51.247 --> 01:00:53.442
Take it easy. Speak slowly. Wah

477
01:00:55.251 --> 01:00:57.185
Wah. hang in there. Wah

478
01:01:05.194 --> 01:01:06.991
I took Wong Po's money...

479
01:01:09.098 --> 01:01:11.123
Chung has been covering
us for a long time

480
01:01:13.569 --> 01:01:15.730
I want to help Chung raise the kid

481
01:01:20.109 --> 01:01:23.840
The money... is in the trunk of Lok's car

482
01:01:39.595 --> 01:01:43.964
We are no good... no good...

483
01:01:48.004 --> 01:01:52.202
Inspector Ma... We've wronged the force

484
01:01:53.176 --> 01:01:54.700
We've wronged Chung...

485
01:01:57.180 --> 01:02:00.980
Where is Chung? Where is he?

486
01:02:02.952 --> 01:02:06.547
Chung... Give Chung the money...

487
01:02:08.124 --> 01:02:09.614
Chung... Chung

488
01:02:48.598 --> 01:02:50.327
They took Wong Po's money

489
01:02:51.067 --> 01:02:52.967
in order to help you raise your daughter

490
01:03:41.784 --> 01:03:43.217
You know why I want to help you?

491
01:03:47.056 --> 01:03:48.421
My father was a cop

492
01:03:51.627 --> 01:03:53.754
I grew up in the police quarters

493
01:03:55.731 --> 01:03:57.892
I watched my father march everyday

494
01:03:59.569 --> 01:04:01.503
And I followed his steps in the balcony

495
01:04:03.206 --> 01:04:05.333
From then on.
I made up my mind to be a cop

496
01:04:09.212 --> 01:04:10.406
One time. my father was handling

497
01:04:10.613 --> 01:04:12.444
a case of smuggling illegal firearms

498
01:04:13.549 --> 01:04:15.312
and he was surrounded by
a gang of outlaws

499
01:04:17.587 --> 01:04:21.455
He got more than 30 shots.
all in his limbs

500
01:04:23.326 --> 01:04:25.260
He died after two hours of struggling

501
01:04:29.432 --> 01:04:32.026
As for the gang. none of them was caught

502
01:04:38.708 --> 01:04:40.175
My father was very superstitious

503
01:04:42.478 --> 01:04:43.945
He said something about me...

504
01:04:44.780 --> 01:04:45.576
"Thy life is governed by
the Ruinous Star.

505
01:04:45.781 --> 01:04:47.715
Be thou a soldier.
and ill fate will befall thee"

506
01:04:49.852 --> 01:04:51.581
With his last breath.
he told me not to be a cop

507
01:04:55.224 --> 01:04:56.748
I don't believe in fate

508
01:04:58.995 --> 01:05:01.361
I only believe there are things
only the police could handle

509
01:05:07.103 --> 01:05:08.764
All three of them were good cops

510
01:05:10.239 --> 01:05:11.433
So are you

511
01:05:20.683 --> 01:05:22.412
I'll go and get the money
from the station

512
01:05:23.786 --> 01:05:25.515
We'll then go and
give it back to Wong Po together

513
01:05:32.495 --> 01:05:33.757
I'll wait for you here

514
01:06:03.092 --> 01:06:06.493
Kwun. do you know
that they tried to frame Wong Po?

515
01:06:07.363 --> 01:06:08.193
I know

516
01:06:08.731 --> 01:06:10.255
You gave the force a bad name!

517
01:06:14.503 --> 01:06:16.835
All that we've done. we've done it
for the reputation of the force

518
01:06:17.673 --> 01:06:19.072
Did you do anything for us?

519
01:06:19.442 --> 01:06:20.841
Did anybody notice.
when they had done theirjob well?

520
01:06:21.978 --> 01:06:23.377
Wong Po has evidence now.

521
01:06:23.579 --> 01:06:25.069
I can't pretend as
if nothing has happened

522
01:06:25.548 --> 01:06:27.038
My men got killed.

523
01:06:27.249 --> 01:06:28.841
and I can't pretend as
if nothing has happened either

524
01:06:33.856 --> 01:06:34.754
Kwun!

525
01:07:21.704 --> 01:07:23.569
Chan Kwok Chung.
give me back my money.

526
01:07:23.773 --> 01:07:24.831
and I'll call it quits

527
01:08:00.876 --> 01:08:01.774
Stop!

528
01:08:35.911 --> 01:08:37.242
God is fair

529
01:08:37.780 --> 01:08:39.771
There would be
consequences for all mistakes

530
01:08:42.818 --> 01:08:44.615
I'll pay you back on behalf of my men

531
01:09:19.788 --> 01:09:22.882
How could you kill. without your gun?

532
01:10:59.488 --> 01:11:00.955
I'm bringing you the thing you want

533
01:11:01.357 --> 01:11:03.382
If Chung is still alive. let him go

534
01:11:14.570 --> 01:11:16.663
I don't know how much longer
he could hang in there

535
01:11:28.884 --> 01:11:30.146
I'll go down to meet him

536
01:19:25.927 --> 01:19:27.360
Honey

537
01:19:31.666 --> 01:19:32.928
I'm all right

538
01:19:41.543 --> 01:19:42.009
Hello?

539
01:19:42.210 --> 01:19:43.438
Honey?

540
01:19:45.714 --> 01:19:46.578
Hello?

541
01:19:49.117 --> 01:19:51.915
Hello? Honey...

542
01:19:54.756 --> 01:19:57.350
Are you all right?
It's so noisy at your end?

543
01:19:59.628 --> 01:20:00.822
Hello?

544
01:20:01.029 --> 01:20:03.361
Honey. both the baby and I
miss you very much

545
01:20:03.598 --> 01:20:04.997
Do you want to talk to the baby?

546
01:20:05.267 --> 01:20:06.199
Honey?

547
01:20:10.038 --> 01:20:11.005
Hello?

548
01:20:12.507 --> 01:20:13.735
Are you all right. honey?

549
01:20:16.711 --> 01:20:19.908
I'm fine. I still have something in hand.
I'll be back soon

550
01:20:20.115 --> 01:20:22.310
The baby and I are just downstairs.
We'll come up

551
01:20:22.517 --> 01:20:25.247
Don't! Wait for me downstairs

552
01:20:25.620 --> 01:20:26.951
Fine

553
01:22:25.373 --> 01:22:27.238
You don't intend to let me down?

554
01:22:34.249 --> 01:22:38.083
You shouldn't come.
We were asking for it

555
01:22:41.423 --> 01:22:43.254
I only want to gain back
some respect for my men

556
01:27:26.541 --> 01:27:27.735
My men are not bad

557
01:27:29.344 --> 01:27:30.606
Who is the most able?

558
01:27:31.145 --> 01:27:32.544
Every one of them is able

559
01:27:32.780 --> 01:27:34.748
Words are empty.
You'll get to know them

560
01:27:36.417 --> 01:27:37.543
My goddaughter

561
01:27:38.686 --> 01:27:40.620
Her parents were killed by Wong Po

562
01:27:42.156 --> 01:27:44.852
I want to take care of her.
but time is running out

